ğŸ”¥ 6. Complete Difference Table (HEAP vs SCP)

| Feature    | **Heap Memory**            | **SCP (String Constant Pool)**          |
| ---------- | -------------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Storage    | All objects                | Only string literals                    |
